<author>sẖạdy ywsf</author>
<lyrics>[C1]
   ạlqrạr- qṣẗ ạlḥb ạlʿjyb qd tjlt fy ạlṣlyb
   qd rwạhạ ly ḥbyby sạʿẗ ạlṣmt ạlrhyb
   whw msḥwq ạlfw̉ạd whw mjrwḥ ạljbyn
   qd rwạhạ ly ḥbyby bạldm ạlgẖạly ạltẖmyn

[V1]
 1- kạn bạlạ̉ms yjwl yṣnʿ ạlkẖyr ạlʿẓym
 wynạdy bạlḥyạẗ ysẖfy jrḥ ạlmtʿbyn
 (kạn ḥbh ʿjybạaⁿ ạ̹dẖạ ạ̉ḥb ạlậtẖmyn
 dẖạ lạ̉nh yswʿ qd ạ̉ḥb kl ḥyn)2

[V2]
 2- bynmạ ạlḥb yjwl kạn fkr ạlḥạqdyn
 kyf yqtlwạ yswʿ ạ̹dẖ ạ̉ḥb ạlmdẖnbyn
 (ḥty̱ yktbwạ ạlnhạyẗ qṣẗ ạlḥb ạtẖmyn
 ḥty̱ tnthy ạlrwạyẗ mạt byn ạlmjrmyn)2

[V3]
 3- ạ̉y ḥb qd tnạhy̱ mtẖl ḥbh ạlʿjyb
 ạ̉y ḥb mtẖl hdẖạ qd bdạ ʿnd ạlṣlyb
 (kl ḥb fy ạlwjwd nbʿh ḥb yswʿ
 kl ḥb fy kyạny rdh ḥb yswʿ)2</lyrics>
<title>qṣẗ ạlḥb ạlʿjyb</title>
</song>